description: Picture perfect 1 bed/1 bath condo with deeded garage parking! Take the elevator up to the second floor and be welcomed by a large, flexible layout that accommodates separate dining, office and/or living areas. Unit features granite and stainless kitchen w/ disposal, a modern marble bath, and beautiful newer hardwood floors. French doors lead to a spacious and sunny bedroom featuring a custom-designed walk-in closet and two juliette balconies provide clear downtown city views and a peek of the water. Top it off with in unit laundry, central A/C, abundant closet space and bonus extra storage near your dedicated parking spot in the heated garage. Perfect location in the heart of vibrant South Boston and walkable to everything. Close in time to enjoy all of what summer in South Boston has to offer!
